   BUGS
   ====
   
   There are no known bugs in Beamsolver. 

   It may be possible to corrupt the solution area of 
   BeamSolver's GUI by using beam variables that cause 
   calculation of extremely high values of shears, moments, 
   stresses, or deflections. Although, I was not able to 
   do so using what I considered to be "very high" input 
   values, no special measures were taken to prevent this 
   from happening.

   Kindly address any bug you may find to the author at the 
   address below, with adequate information to resolve the
   problem.


   COMMENTS
   ========
   
   BeamSolver is likely to appeal to a only a very small 
   audience; still, I would be much pleased to hear any 
